Problem:

Users often know how they feel but don't know what to search for.

Solution:

Allow users to describe their mood in natural language.

Examples:-

"Need music while coding."

"Relax after work."

"Workout motivation."

Spotify generates personalized playlists using:

Listening history
Time of day
Weather (optional)
Activity
Favorite artists


